_meanings:
{@--1@} To join, unite, attach,
connect. add; {#tamarTamiva BAratyA sutayA#}
{#yoktumarhasi#} <ls>Ku. 6. 79</ls>; see {%<ab>pass.</ab>%} 
below.

{@--2@} To yoke, harness, put to;
{#BAnuH sakfdyuktaturaMga eva#} <ls>Ś. 5. 4</ls>;  
<ls>Bg. 1. 14.</ls>

{@--4@} To use, employ,
apply; {#praSaste karmaRi taTA sacCabdaH#}
{#pArTa yujyate#} <ls>Bg. 17. 26</ls>; <ls>Ms. 7. 204.</ls>

{@--6@}
To direct, turn or fix upon (as the
mind &c.).

{@--7@} To concentrate one's
attention upon; {#manaH saMyamya maccitto#}
{#yukta AsIta matparaH#} <ls>Bg. 6. 14</ls>;  
{#yuMjannevaM sadAtmAnaM#} <ls n="Bg. 6.">15.</ls>

{@--1@} To be joined or
united with; {#ravipItajalA tapAtyaye#}
{#punaroGena hi yujyate nadI#} <ls>Ku. 4. 44</ls>;  
<ls>R. 8. 17.</ls>

{@--2@} To get, be possessed of;
{#izwEryujyeTAM#} <ls>Mv. 7</ls>; {#izwena yujyasva#} <ls>Ś. 5</ls>;
<ls>R. 3. 65.</ls>

{@--3@} To be fit or right, be
proper, to suit (with <ab>loc.</ab> or <ab>gen.</ab>);
{#yA yasya yujyate BUmikA tAM Kalu BAvena#}
{#taTEva sarve vargyAH pAWitAH#} <ls>Māl. 1</ls>;  
{#trElokyasyApi praButvaM tvayi yujyate#} <ls>H. 1.</ls>

{@--4@}
To be ready for; {#tatA yudDAya yujyasva#}
<ls>Bg. 2. 38</ls>, <ls n="Bg. 2.">50.</ls>

{@--5@} To be intent on,
be absorbed in, be directed towards;
<ls>Ms. 3. 75</ls>, <ls n="Ms.">14. 35</ls>; <ls>Ki. 7. 13.</ls>

{@--1@}
To join, unite, bring together;  
{#paraspareRa spfhaRIyaSoBaM na cedidaM#} 
{#dvaMdvamayojayizyat#} <ls>R. 7. 14.</ls>

{@--3@} To appoint,
employ, use; {#SatruBiryojayicCatruM#}  
<ls>Pt. 4. 17.</ls>

{@--4@} To turn or direct towards;
{#pApAnnivArayati yojayate hitAya#}  
<ls>Bh. 2. 72.</ls>

To concentrate
the mind (identical with the {%<ab>pass.</ab>%}
of {#yuj#} I).
